All Classes

Class Description
AddCarController
Controller class for the add car window.
AddCustomerController
Controller class for the add customer window.
Car
Represents a car.
CarType
Different types of cars that can have a Car object.
Customer
This Class Holds Data for Customers who are renting a Car, its also inherits it's data to Classes Resident and Visitor.
FCarsRentalSystem
The main application class for the rental system.
FileProcessing
Unified file processing class that allows to separate the file processing methods from the main system classes.
Invoice
Invoice class contains methods to add, modify or delete payments stores along with their dates
MainCarController
Controller class for the main car window showing details of all the cars and also buttons to add, update or delete a car.
MainCustomerController
Controller class for the main customer window showing details of all the customers and also buttons to add, update or delete a customer.
MainRentalController
Controller class for the main rental window.
MainUIController
Controller class for the main UI window of the application.
Payment
Payment class contains getters and setters for the provided instance variables that are used by the invoice class
Rental
Represents a car rental from the rental system.
Resident
This Class inherits from the Customer Class, It holds Data for Customers who are Residents of the Country and With a Valid ID card.
UpdateCarController
Controller class for the update car window.
UpdateCustomerController
Controller class for the update customer window.
Visitor
This Class inherits from the Customer Class, It holds Data for Customers who are visitors to the Country.
